    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A caption with an article on May 15 about the trial of Jose Padilla, who is charged with conspiring to support terrorism, incorrectly rendered the name of his mother, who was shown outside federal court in Miami. She is Estela Ortega-Lebron, not Estrela Ortega. The article also misstated the year of his transfer from military custody to civilian custody. It was 2006, not 2005.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
